{"lemma":"سَلَّةٍ","slug":"سَلَّةٍ","root":"س.ل.ل","root_slug":"س-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ل-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n20290","n20291"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"instance noun of سَلّ (sall, “drawing out”)."},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"basket"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sweetvetch (Hedysarum spp.)"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun of سَلّ (sall, “drawing out”).\n\nBorrowed from Aramaic סַלְּתָא (salləṯā, “basket”).\n\nBorrowed from Classical Syriac ܣܠܬܐ (seltā, “moss, lichen, seawead; a contemptible plant”); compare Hebrew סִלֹּון (sillōn, “briar”)."},"ipa":["/sil.la/","/sul.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n20290","headword_ar":"سَلَّةٌ","root":"sl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drawing of swords;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sil~apN","text_ar":"سِلَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) So in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayonaAhumo Einoda Als~al~api","text_ar":"اَتَيْنَاهُمْ عِنْدَ السَّلَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We came to them on the occasion of the drawing of swords"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, M, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Theft:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covert, secret,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clandestine, theft;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_isolaAlN","text_ar":"اـِسْلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[except that the former is a simple subst., and the latter is an inf. n., i. e. of 4]: (K:) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY baniY fulaAnK sal~apN","text_ar":"فِى بَنِى فُلَانٍ سَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Among the sons of such a one is theft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covert theft"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxal~apu tadoEuw A_ilaY Als~al~api","text_ar":"الخَلَّةُ تَدْعُو اـِلَى السَّلَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Want invites to theft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covert theft"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)       -A2-  Also (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rush"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dufoEap","text_ar":"دُفْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":") of a horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among other horses, in running:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rush"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dufoEap","text_ar":"دُفْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":") of a horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in striving to outstrip:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA: [I read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY sibaAqihi","text_ar":"فِى سِبَاقِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in a copy of the S; instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY siyaAqihi","text_ar":"فى سِيَاقِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in other copies of the S and in the TA:]) so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farasN $adiydu Als~al~api","text_ar":"فَرَسٌ شَدِيدُ السَّلَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A horse of which the rush"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is vehement"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarajato sal~atuhu EalaY","text_ar":"خَرَجَتْ سَلَّتُهُ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxayoli","text_ar":"الخَيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY saAy^iri Alxayoli","text_ar":"عَلَى سَايِرِ الخَيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His rush in striving to outstrip proceeded against the other horses"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A revulsion of shortness of breathing"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirotidaAdu rabowK","text_ar":"اِرْتِدَادُ رَبْوٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the chest of a horse, in consequence of his suppressing such shortness of breathing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so I render"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino kabowapK yakobuwhaA","text_ar":"مِنْ كَبْوَةٍ يَكْبُوهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this phrase admits of other renderings, as will be seen in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kbw","text_ar":"كبو"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M, K:) when he is inflated thereby, one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoraja sal~atahu","text_ar":"اَخْرَجَ سَلَّتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he has manifested his revulsion of shortness of breathing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and thereupon he is urged to run with vehemence, and made to sweat, and coverings are thrown upon him, and that shortness of breathing ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*`lika Alr~abowu","text_ar":"ذٰلِكَ الرَّبْوُ"},{"kind":"text","text":") passes forth. (M.) ―         -b3-  [In a sheep or goat, or a ewe or she-goat, it seems to mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force, of long continuance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoluwlapN","text_ar":"مَسْلُولَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoluwlN","text_ar":"مَسْلُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sil~N","text_ar":"سِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"basket of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juwnap","text_ar":"جُونَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juwnap","text_ar":"جُونَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the covered"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juwnap","text_ar":"جُونَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saba*apN","text_ar":"سَبَذَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; so says Az: (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a receptacle in which fruit is carried:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sometimes covered with red skin:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawarN","text_ar":"حَوَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) in the present day commonly applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a basket made of twigs, oblong and deep, generally between a foot and a foot and a half in length:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sal~N","text_ar":"سَلٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (M, K:) what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sal~apu Alxubozi","text_ar":"سَلَّةُ الخُبْزِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the bread-basket"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is well known: (S:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sal~apN","text_ar":"سَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning as expl. above is not thought by IDrd to be an Arabic word: (M:) [the dim. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sulayolapN","text_ar":"سُلَيْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in the K voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juwnapN","text_ar":"جُونَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and in the Mgh voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raboEapN","text_ar":"رَبْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.:] the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"silaAlN","text_ar":"سِلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sal~aAtN","text_ar":"سَلَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) and [coll. gen. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sal~N","text_ar":"سَلٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1397},{"kind":"text","text":"which Abu-l-Hasan says that it is in his opinion a rare kind of pl. [or coll. gen. n.] because it denotes what is made by art, not created, and it should more properly be regarded as of the class of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawokabN","text_ar":"كَوْكَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawokabapN","text_ar":"كَوْكَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which are syn.] because this is more common than the class of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safiynapN","text_ar":"سَفِينَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safiynN","text_ar":"سَفِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.)       -A5-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A fault,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defect, in a water-ing-trough"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tank,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"jar of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAbiyap","text_ar":"خَابِيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a breach between the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anoSaAbi","text_ar":"اَنْصَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or [more properly]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSaAy^ib","text_ar":"نَصَايِب"},{"kind":"text","text":", [i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stones set up, and cemented together with kneaded clay, around the interior,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a watering-trough"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tank."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fissures in the ground, that steal"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"imbibe"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A6-  Also One's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sewing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a skin, or hide,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two thongs in a single puncture,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stitch-hole."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA","M"]},{"entry_id":"n20291","headword_ar":"سِلَّةٌ","root":"sl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sal~apN","text_ar":"سَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}